songs.title: Rollercoaster
songs.lyrics:
Get so high
Go so fast
It's getting good

I wanna make it last
Spinning round
Soaring Free
Steady now your gonna make me scream and shout
Tryin land it's rushing down
But light and sound is spinning round
Tryin land it's pouring out
You make me want to scream and shout
You got me going around in circles
Like a rollercoaster
You got me going around in circles
Like a rollercoaster
You got me going around in circles
Like a rollercoaster
You got me going around in circles
Like a rollercoaster
You make
You make
You make me go round
You make me
You make
Go round
